{"ts":"2026-06-27T03:14:24.144Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"tool","toolName":"run_commands","toolCallId":"f43snsru","output":[{"query":"git diff automation/tasks.json","result":"diff --git a/automation/tasks.json b/automation/tasks.json\nindex 350a062..5ea88f6 100644\n--- a/automation/tasks.json\n+++ b/automation/tasks.json\n@@ -621,7 +621,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-data\",\n     \"target\": \"local mock data\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Create a local mock data model for the client portal and admin portal. Do not add a database or backend. Do not create fake real customer data that implies actual clients. Use clearly representative data and label it as preview/demo data where surfaced. Data should support dashboard, projects, AI operations, documents, billing/invoices, support tickets, analytics, governance, users, clients, activity feed, and notifications. Include types for ClientAccount, Project, AgentOperation, DocumentItem, Invoice, SupportTicket, AnalyticsMetric, GovernanceItem, User, Role. Include deterministic sample entries such as representative client account, representative project names, representative agent names, preview invoices, preview tickets. No fake logos or real client names. Centralize in a safe local data file. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Data should support dashboard, projects, AI operations, documents, billing/invoices, support tickets, governance, users, and clients. Include types for ClientAccount, Project, AgentOperation, DocumentItem, Invoice, SupportTicket, GovernanceItem, User, Role.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"78-phase4-data-table-filter-system\",\n@@ -629,7 +629,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-component\",\n     \"target\": \"tables lists filters\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build reusable premium table, list, filter, and detail-drawer components for portal and admin pages. Do not touch landing page. Components should support search, status filters, type filters, sort controls, empty state, row click, mobile card fallback, and accessible keyboard navigation. Use these components for Projects, Documents, Billing, Support, Users, Clients, AI Operations, Governance, and Activity. Make the design feel custom and expensive, not default HTML tables. Use subtle row hover, sticky header where useful, and clean responsive cards on mobile. No backend calls. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build reusable premium table, list, filter, and detail-drawer components for portal and admin pages. Do not touch landing page. Components should support search, status filters, type filters, sort controls, empty state, row click, mobile card fallback, and accessible keyboard navigation. Use these components for Projects, Documents, Billing, Support, Users, Clients, AI Operations, Governance. Make the design feel custom and expensive, not default HTML tables. Use subtle row hover, sticky header where useful, and clean responsive cards on mobile. No backend calls. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"79-phase4-client-dashboard\",\n@@ -653,7 +653,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-client-portal\",\n     \"target\": \"/portal/ai-operations\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/ai-operations as the client-facing AI operations command center. Do not touch landing page. Include agent health overview, managed AI operations status, active agents, human review queue preview, governance checks, runtime status, adoption indicators, spend preview, incident/issue preview, and Control Center link. Use labels and representative preview data only. Do not claim real-time operations. Use premium dashboard UI with status rails, agent cards, health rings, timeline, and tabs. Add filters by project, agent type, status, and operating stage. No backend. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/ai-operations as the client-facing AI operations command center. Do not touch landing page. Include agent health overview, managed AI operations status, active agents,governance checks, runtime status and Control Center link. Use labels and representative preview data only. Do not claim real-time operations. Use premium dashboard UI with status rails, agent cards, health rings, timeline, and tabs. Add filters by project, agent type, status, and operating stage. No backend. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"84-phase4-client-documents-library\",\n@@ -661,7 +661,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-client-portal\",\n     \"target\": \"/portal/documents\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/documents as a premium document library for clients. Do not touch landing page. Include document search, category filters, project filters, document type filters, status filters, recent uploads preview, pinned documents, and document cards/table. Categories may include Proposals, SOW, Architecture, Reports, Invoices, Governance, Meeting Notes, Delivery Assets. No real file upload or download. Add disabled or preview upload button with future backend note. Add document preview drawer with metadata, related project, version, owner, and activity. Use representative data only. Mobile must be excellent. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/documents as a premium document library for clients. Do not touch landing page. Include document search, category filters, project filters, document type filters, status filters, and document cards/table. Categories may include Proposals, SOW, Architecture, Reports, Invoices, Governance, Meeting Notes, Delivery Assets. No real file upload or download. Add disabled or preview upload button with future backend note. Add document preview drawer with metadata, related project, version, owner, and activity. Use representative data only. Mobile must be excellent. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"86-phase4-client-billing-overview\",\n@@ -669,7 +669,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-client-portal\",\n     \"target\": \"/portal/billing and /portal/billing/invoices\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/billing and /portal/billing/invoices as premium billing and invoice preview pages. Do not touch landing page. Include billing summary, invoice list, invoice status, due date, project association, amount preview, payment status preview, and billing contact card. Use representative preview data only. Do not integrate payments. Do not claim real invoices. Add frontend-only actions such as View invoice preview, Copy invoice reference, Contact finance, and Download disabled with backend note. Include filters and mobile card layout. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/billing and /portal/billing/invoices as premium billing and invoice preview pages. Do not touch landing page. Include billing summary, invoice list, invoice status, due date, project association, amount preview, and billing contact card. Use representative preview data only. Do not integrate payments. Do not claim real invoices. Add frontend-only actions such as View invoice preview, Copy invoice reference, Contact finance. Include filters and mobile card layout. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"88-phase4-client-support-center\",\n@@ -677,7 +677,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-client-portal\",\n     \"target\": \"/portal/support\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/support as a premium support center for clients. Do not touch landing page. Include ticket list, create ticket frontend-only form, priority, category, linked project, linked document optional, status filters, support SLA preview copy without guarantees, knowledge/help cards, and recent support activity. No backend submission. On create, add ticket locally in current browser state or show preview-created state. Ticket categories: Project Delivery, AI Operations, Billing, Documents, Access, Governance, General. UI should feel calm, secure, and operational. Mobile excellent. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/support as a premium support center for clients. Do not touch landing page. Include ticket list, create ticket frontend-only form, priority, category, linked project, status filters. No backend submission. On create, add ticket locally in current browser state or show preview-created state. Ticket categories: Project Delivery, AI Operations, Billing, Documents, Access, Governance, General. UI should feel calm, secure, and operational. Mobile excellent. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"91-phase4-client-governance\",\n@@ -685,7 +685,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-client-portal\",\n     \"target\": \"/portal/governance\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/governance as a premium governance workspace. Do not touch landing page. Include governance overview, policy items, approvals, risk reviews, human oversight points, AI operation governance checks, document governance, audit-readiness preview, and activity timeline. Do not make legal or compliance guarantees. Use language like designed to support governance workflows. Include filters by project, agent, status, and severity. Add approval cards and local preview actions such as mark reviewed in browser state only. No backend. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /portal/governance as a premium governance workspace. Do not touch landing page. Include governance overview, policy items, human oversight points, AI operation governance checks, document governance. Do not make legal or compliance guarantees. Use language like designed to support governance workflows. Include filters by project, agent, status, and severity. No backend. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"94-phase4-admin-dashboard\",\n@@ -693,7 +693,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-admin\",\n     \"target\": \"/admin and /admin/dashboard\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /admin and /admin/dashboard as the GFF internal admin control center. Do not touch landing page. Use the private app shell with admin navigation. The dashboard should include clients overview, active projects, AI operations overview, pending support tickets, billing status, governance alerts, user/team activity, recent documents, and operational activity feed. Use representative preview data only. No backend. No fake live metrics. The admin dashboard should feel powerful, dense but elegant, and built for internal delivery operations. Use bento layout, command actions, data cards, charts with preview labels, and strong navigation. Mobile must remain usable. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /admin and /admin/dashboard as the GFF internal admin control center. Do not touch landing page. Use the private app shell with admin navigation. The dashboard should include clients overview, active projects, AI operations overview, pending support tickets, billing status, governance alerts. Use representative preview data only. No backend. No fake live metrics. The admin dashboard should feel powerful, dense but elegant, and built for internal delivery operations. Use bento layout, command actions, data cards, and strong navigation. Mobile must remain usable. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"95-phase4-admin-clients-list\",\n@@ -709,7 +709,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-admin\",\n     \"target\": \"/admin/projects\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Build /admin/projects as internal project delivery management. Do not touch landing page. Include project table/cards with client, phase, status, delivery owner, timeline, next milestone. Add filters by client, phase, status, owner, risk. Add frontend-only actions: create project preview, update status locally. No backend. Make UI premium and dense but readable. Include mobile card fallback. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Build /admin/projects as internal project delivery management. Do not touch landing page. Include project table/cards with client, phase, status, delivery owner. Add filters by client, phase, status, owner, risk. Add frontend-only actions: create project preview, update status locally. No backend. Make UI premium and dense but readable. Include mobile card fallback. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n   {\n     \"id\": \"99-phase4-admin-users-rbac\",\n@@ -797,7 +797,7 @@\n     \"scope\": \"phase4-routing-qa\",\n     \"target\": \"portal admin links\",\n     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n-    \"prompt\": \"Audit and fix all links in login, client portal, admin portal, private sidebar, topbar, command center, notifications, tables, cards, CTAs, breadcrumbs, and detail drawers. Do not touch landing page. Verify all links resolve to explicit routes. No slug route references. /portal must be the Client Login landing. /portal/login and /login must work. Client portal modules must include Dashboard, Projects, AI Operations, Documents, Billing or Invoices, Support, Analytics, Governance. Admin modules must include Dashboard, Clients, Projects, Users, AI Operations, Documents, Billing, Support, Analytics, Governance, Settings. Fix broken links only. Run lint and build.\"\n+    \"prompt\": \"Audit and fix all links in login, client portal, admin portal, private sidebar, topbar, command center, notifications, tables, cards, CTAs, breadcrumbs, and detail drawers. Do not touch landing page. Verify all links resolve to explicit routes. No slug route references. /portal must be the Client Login landing. /portal/login and /login must work. Client portal modules must include Dashboard, Projects, AI Operations, Documents, Billing or Invoices, Support, Analytics, Governance. Admin modules must include Dashboard, Clients, Projects, Users, AI Operations, Documents, Billing, Support, Analytics, Governance. Fix broken links only. Run lint and build.\"\n   },\n