{"ts":"2026-06-27T03:14:28.445Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Analyzing Design Aesthetics**\n\nI'm now analyzing the design aesthetics. It avoids generic templates through custom narratives and specialized layouts. The story of an isolated sandbox auditing environment is clearly told. There's page-specific visual thinking: mobile nav mimics iOS, sidebar uses collapsible states and animations. The dark theme is used consistently but isn't a lazy copy; it feels high-end, with crisp borders and `#009DFF` highlights. The layout avoids unnecessary nesting, opting for clean lines and subtle hover effects instead.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T03:14:29.912Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Evaluating Visual Detail**\n\nI'm now evaluating the visual detail. I am glad that there is minimal usage of \"pills\" and badges. The design avoids fake elements, using representative names and role-specific pathways instead. I am pleased with the integration of useful interactions like Framer Motion animations and hover micro-interactions, particularly on mobile with the customized floating bottom bar and drawer. Spacing is clean via Tailwind, and monospace fonts are being used.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
